{
  "stem": "25598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was-- I started to be afraid of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I just--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes I was afraid to go out in the dark by myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes I was afraid of noises that were not familiar, or I became much more aware of what's happening around me than I was before.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before, I was sort of in a dream, in a daydream, and everything was nice and beautiful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, I was hit with a reality, which wasn't that nice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was told to keep quiet in school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was told not to complain in school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the students usually take after the teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if the teacher says that you-- you're not good because you have blue eyes, or because of whatever, then the students will say the same thing, that you're not good because you have brown eyes, or because you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that they said anything, but the attitude changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like we didn't laugh together, or play together, or run together that much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't come to the house anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't meet in the park anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't go mountain climbing together, to the extent to which at the age of nine or 10 we could mountain climb.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we always-- everybody had a rucksack there, and everybody was going up to the mountains to watch the town in the valley, and to, to gather berries, and to listen to the music in the gazebos.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all that finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also, there were soldiers that-- there were more soldiers in town, Romanian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So going to the park was no longer a pleasure because the people were afraid of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because the, the Iron Guard and the government-- Antonescu's government in Romania-- was very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
